[thinking] 
[thinking] I need to figure out the dependencies. Our JLine version 2 might not be cached, so I could query Maven via Gradle without running tests. It seems I shouldn't run tests but can inspect them. I wonder if I can use curl, though maybe no network is needed. I might need to add a separate dependency with a relocated artifact. JLine version 1's coordinates seem to be jline:jline:0.9.94. I could also explore using org.python:jline?
